    "text": "## Dosage / serving suggestions\n\n| Usage type | Suggested amount |\n|---|---|\n| Tea or warm water | 1 to 2 teaspoons |\n| Toast or breakfast foods | 1 to 2 tablespoons |\n| Smoothies or yogurt | 1 tablespoon |\n| Homemade desserts | Adjust to taste |\n| Family recipes | Use as needed |",
