    "text": "## What to avoid\n\n- Avoid using a wet spoon inside the jar.\n- Do not store the honey in direct sunlight or near high heat.\n- Avoid overheating honey during cooking for long periods.\n- Keep the lid tightly closed after use.\n- Honey is not recommended for infants under 12 months old.\n```",
